org.apache.beam.sdk.values.reflect

Interface FieldValueGetter<T>


  • @Internal
public interface FieldValueGetter<T>
    For internal use only; no backwards-compatibility guarantees.

    An interface to access a field of a class.

    Implementations of this interface are generated at runtime by RowFactory to map pojo fields to BeamRecord fields.
